SQL query of the view VMDR_MDR_META_DADO_REL

SELECT MDR.MDR_ID, MDR.ITR_ID, MDR_CD_ORDEM, MDR.MDR_DS_CHAVE, MDR.MDR_AN_VALOR, MDR.MDR_AN_VALOR_DEFAULT, MDR.MDR_CD_OPER_ATUALZ, MDR.MDR_DH_ATUALZ, MDR.MDR_NU_VERSAO FROM SUP.MDR_META_DADO_REL MDR
INNER JOIN SUP.DAR_DADO_RELATORIO DAR ON MDR.MDR_ID = DAR.MDR_ID
INNER JOIN SUP.REL_RELATORIO_APS REL ON DAR.REL_ID = REL.REL_ID
INNER JOIN SUP.INE_INSPECAO_ENTIDADE INE ON REL.INE_ID = INE.INE_ID
WHERE INE.INE_CD_STATUS = 3
AND (INE.INE_DH_PUBLICACAO >= '2015-01-01' AND INE.INE_DH_PUBLICACAO < '2018-01-01')
